✅ 正確完整流程範例（可直接用）
Step 1️⃣ 先取得 CSRF Token + Cookie
var baseUrl = "https://sapserver";
var serviceUrl = "/sap/opu/odata/sap/ZMY_SRV/";

var handler = new HttpClientHandler
{
    Credentials = new NetworkCredential("SAP_USER", "SAP_PASSWORD"),
    UseCookies = true,
    CookieContainer = new CookieContainer()
};

using var client = new HttpClient(handler);

var fetchRequest = new HttpRequestMessage(HttpMethod.Get, baseUrl + serviceUrl);
fetchRequest.Headers.Add("X-CSRF-Token", "Fetch");

var fetchResponse = await client.SendAsync(fetchRequest);
fetchResponse.EnsureSuccessStatusCode();

var csrfToken = fetchResponse.Headers
    .FirstOrDefault(h => h.Key.Equals("X-CSRF-Token", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
    .Value?.FirstOrDefault();

if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(csrfToken))
    throw new Exception("CSRF Token not found");


👉 這裡 Cookie 已經自動存進 handler.CookieContainer（重點！）

Step 2️⃣ 用同一個 HttpClient 送 POST
var postUrl = baseUrl + serviceUrl + "EntitySet"; // 你的 OData Entity

var postData = new
{
    Field1 = "Value1",
    Field2 = "Value2"
};

var json = JsonSerializer.Serialize(postData);

var postRequest = new HttpRequestMessage(HttpMethod.Post, postUrl);
postRequest.Headers.Add("X-CSRF-Token", csrfToken);
postRequest.Headers.Add("Accept", "application/json");

postRequest.Content = new StringContent(json, Encoding.UTF8, "application/json");

var postResponse = await client.SendAsync(postRequest);
var result = await postResponse.Content.ReadAsStringAsync();

Console.WriteLine(postResponse.StatusCode);
Console.WriteLine(result);

❗你剛剛那段 code 少了什麼？

你原本這樣拿 Cookie：

var cookies = response.Headers.GetValues("Set-Cookie");


但你 沒有把它加回下一個 Request

👉 其實 根本不用手動處理 Cookie！
只要：

UseCookies = true,
CookieContainer = new CookieContainer()


而且同一個 HttpClient 不要 new 第二次
SAP Session 就會自動帶著走

💥 常見踩雷點
錯誤行為	結果
取 Token 用一個 HttpClient，POST 用另一個	403
沒開 UseCookies	403
Token 有效但沒帶 Cookie	403
Cookie 有但沒帶 Token	403
POST 忘記 Content-Type: application/json	415
🧪 成功時你會看到
狀態碼	代表
201 Created	新增成功
204 NoContent	更新成功
403 Forbidden	少 CSRF 或 Cookie
401 Unauthorized	帳密錯
🎯 一句話總結

SAP OData =「登入憑證 + CSRF Token + Session Cookie」三件套一起用，而且必須是同一個 HttpClient

